import React from "react";

const DashboardIcon = () => {
  return (
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="13.525"
      height="13.525"
      viewBox="0 0 13.525 13.525"
    >
      <g
        id="Icon_feather-sidebar"
        data-name="Icon feather-sidebar"
        transform="translate(-3.9 -3.9)"
      >
        <path
          id="Tracé_6"
          data-name="Tracé 6"
          d="M5.869,4.5h9.586a1.369,1.369,0,0,1,1.369,1.369v9.586a1.369,1.369,0,0,1-1.369,1.369H5.869A1.369,1.369,0,0,1,4.5,15.455V5.869A1.369,1.369,0,0,1,5.869,4.5Z"
          fill="none"
          stroke="#100f0f"
          strokeLinecap="round"
          strokeLinejoin="round"
          strokeWidth="1.2"
        />
        <path
          id="Tracé_7"
          data-name="Tracé 7"
          d="M13.5,4.5V16.825"
          transform="translate(-4.892)"
          fill="none"
          stroke="#100f0f"
          strokeLinecap="round"
          strokeLinejoin="round"
          strokeWidth="1.2"
        />
      </g>
    </svg>
  );
};

export default DashboardIcon;
